Package: centrcanon
Title: Analytical Engine for CEnTR*MAP Community-Engaged Research Mapping
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jeremy", "Price",
           email = "jfprice@iu.edu",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides the core analytical pipelines for CEnTR*MAP, a workflow
    for mapping the conceptual landscape of community-engaged research (CEnR).
    Implements three complementary pipelines: anchoring (correspondence
    analysis and PAM clustering), integration (network centrality), and
    leverage (key actor classification). The package is designed to be called
    from a Shiny application but works entirely from the R console.
